| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3517 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5904db3a-847f-5bc0-aa5a-a9557a537d5d"
